{
    "678:0": "atha catuścatvāriṃśaḥ paṭalavisaraḥ |",
    "678:1": "atha khalu bhagavāṃ śākyamuniḥ punarapi śuddhāvāsabhavanamavalokya sarvatathāgatadharmavarotvacintyaguṇavyūhālaṅkārabhūtakoṭiniṣṭhāsaṅkhyeyajinamudrāmudritaṃ sarvasattvacihnabhūtaṃ mudrāpaṭalaparamaguhyatamaṃ sarvalaukikalokottaraśreyasamantratantrakalpavikalpitaṃ sarvasattvaiḥ paramārthadarśanapathapravṛttibhūtaṃ sarvamantrasarvasaṃjñāsādhāraṇabhūtamihaiva janmani sarvasattvānāṃ sarvāśāpāripūrakaṃ sarvabuddhabodhisattvānāmārādhanaparasukhahetukabodhisambhāraparipūraṇanimittam āhvānanavisarjanagandhapuṣpadhūpasarvamālyopahārāvidyāvidyā-",
    "678:2": "veśanadarśanasarvakāryārthasādhanasarvadevanāgayakṣagandharvāsuragaruḍakinnara-mahoragayakṣarākṣasapiśācakūṣmāṇḍaraudrasaumyabhāvadamakādhyakṣabhūtādhi-patisarvakāryasandarśanajvalanākāśagamanāntarddhānavaśīkaraṇabodhisambhāranimittāścaryādbhutaṃ sarvamantratantrārtthānunītaṃ sarvavidyārājanamaskṛtaṃ sarvavidyāsādhakaṃ sarvabuddhamātrāmantritaṃ yathepsitārtthasattvamanorathāparipūrakaṃ sarvāsāṃ sarvamantrāṇāṃ dṛṣṭadhārmikahetuniṣpādakaṃ saṃkṣepato yathā yathā yujyate,",
    "678:3": "yathā yathā sādhyate tathā tathā sādhayate |",
    "678:4": "eṣā mañjuśrīḥ ! paramārtthapaṭalasarvabuddhānāṃ paramārtthaguhyatamaṃ bhāṣiṣye |",
    "678:5": "pūrvaṃ bhāṣitavāṃ sarvabuddhaiḥ bhāṣiṣyante'nāgatā buddhā bhagavantaḥ |",
    "678:6": "etarhyahaṃ bhāṣiṣye,",
    "678:7": "tacchrūyatāṃ mahāsattva ! bhāṣiṣye |",
    "678:8": "tacchrūyatāṃ mahāsattva ! bhāṣiṣye |",
    "678:9": "sādhu ca suṣṭhu ca manasi kuru mañjurava ! manojñapratibhānavāṃ vakṣye'haṃ vakṣye'hamiti ||",
    "678:10": "śākyasiṃha naraśreṣṭho sambuddho ṛṣisattamaḥ |",
    "678:11": "sattvamartthamabhijñāya paramārtthārtthadarśanam ||",
    "678:12": "guhyamātrārtthamudrā vai bhāṣase munipuṅgava ! |",
    "678:13": "śuddhāvāsapure ramye śuddhasattvasamāśrite ||",
    "678:14": "samāparṣadvare śreṣṭhe vītarāgālaye tadā |",
    "678:15": "bhāṣite kalparāje tu mañjubhāgītatattvite ||",
    "678:16": "buddhaputraistadāmātyaiḥ paramārtthavidairvidaiḥ |",
    "678:17": "śākyasiṃhastadā āha śṛṇudhvaṃ parṣat kathe ||",
    "678:18": "buddhaputrastathā jyeṣṭha mahāyānāgradharmiṇaḥ |",
    "678:19": "nāmnā samantabhadro vai ityuvāca girāṃ varām ||",
    "678:20": "bālarūpī mahārūpī kumārastvaṃ varṇyase jinaiḥ |",
    "678:21": "śākyasya kulajo dakṣaḥ śrīmāṃ buddho nirīkṣyate ||",
    "678:22": "tvaṃ hi viśvamahāprājño lokānugrahakāmyayā |",
    "678:23": "tvadīyaṃ kalpavisaraṃ mudrāmudritaṃ tvidam ||",
    "678:24": "adhyeṣaya mahāvīraṃ ! buddhaputra ! maharddhika |",
    "678:25": "sārabhūtaṃ kalpasyāsya maharddhikam ||",
    "678:26": "evamuktastu vīreṇa buddhaputreṇa dhīmatā |",
    "678:27": "mañjumāṃ tvarito jāta bālakrīḍābhinirmita ||",
    "678:28": "praṇamya sugataṃ nāthaṃ jagadekāntacakṣuṣam |",
    "678:29": "uvāca madhurāṃ vāṇīṃ karuṇārdramreḍitena tu ||",
    "678:30": "kathayeyu bhagavāṃ buddhaḥ prajñābalatattvavit |",
    "678:31": "kathaṃ tu sarvamantrā vai siddhyanti japināṃ dhruvam ||",
    "678:32": "kathaṃ vai hyavikalpena amoghān gacchanti prāṇinām |",
    "678:33": "siddhyeyuḥ kṣiptajaptābhiḥ sarvārttheṣu na yojitā ||",
    "678:34": "ā bhavāgrācca saṃsārādā vīcyāntāśca nārakāḥ |",
    "678:35": "eteṣvāśritā ye ca prāṇinordhatridhātukā ||",
    "678:36": "āhūyante nigṛhyante āveśyante ca paśyatām |",
    "678:37": "sarvakarmārtthayukte ca tuṣṭipuṣṭyarthakāraṇaiḥ ||",
    "678:38": "daśabhūmyāśritā ye ca saugate vartmani sthitā |",
    "678:39": "bodhisattvā vibuddhāśca pratyekāṃ vā bodhimāśritāḥ ||",
    "678:40": "vītarāga mahātmana āhūyante supūjitā |",
    "678:41": "samayairmantribhiryuktā imairmudraiḥ samudritā ||",
    "678:42": "kathayanti yathābhūtaṃ svatantrā cāpi darśinam |",
    "678:43": "pūrvavṛttamavṛttaṃ vā vartamāne ca yoginaḥ ||",
    "678:44": "svargalokakathācintyā paradehāśritāpi vā |",
    "678:45": "anāgataṃ ca yathātatthyaṃ nidarśanaṃ cāpi varṇitam ||",
    "678:46": "kathayanti yathānyāyaṃ mantramudrasamīritā |",
    "678:47": "siddhiṃ cāpi tathā kṣipraṃ dadyānmudraiśca pūjitāḥ ||",
    "678:48": "mantrijñaiḥ mantribhiryuktaḥ balihomasupūjitāḥ |",
    "678:49": "kuryāt kṣiprataraṃ siddhiṃ buddhā buddhasutāstathā ||",
    "678:50": "arhanto'pi mahātmānaḥ khaḍgiṇaḥ siddhidā sadā |",
    "678:51": "laukikā ye ca mantrā vai tathā lokottarā pare ||",
    "678:52": "ye ca siddhāstathā yakṣā gandharvā matha kinnarā |",
    "678:53": "asurā surā sadā sattvā sarvasattvā tridhā sthitā ||",
    "678:54": "aparyanteṣu dikṣveṣu lokadhātvantareṣu ca |",
    "678:55": "gatipañcasu ye sattvā yuktāyuktāśca sarvadā ||",
    "678:56": "siddhiṃ gaccheyu tat kṣipraṃ imairmudraiḥ sumudritā |",
    "678:57": "eṣa vikhyātaḥ sugatairmantrajñaistu munibhiḥ vimalam ||",
    "678:58": "viṭakaṃ vidhivad jñeyaṃ visaraṃ paṭalottamam |",
    "678:59": "sarvabuddhaistathā loke śreyasārthamudāhṛtā ||",
    "678:60": "mudrā pañcaśikhetyāhuḥ sarvabuddhaiḥ prakāśitā |",
    "678:61": "śreyasārthaṃ hi bhūtānāṃ mañjughoṣasya dhīmate ||",
    "678:62": "sarvataḥ śirajā jñeyā mūrdhnajāstu tathāgatām |",
    "678:63": "sā tu sarvārthadā jñeyā dharmakośaprapūraṇī ||",
    "678:64": "pūraṇārthaṃ tu mantrāṇāṃ mudrāṇāṃ ca maharddhikam |",
    "678:65": "sarveṣāṃ lokottarāṃ śreṣṭhāṃ laukikānāṃ ca sarvadā ||",
    "678:66": "mañjughoṣasya tantre tu agrā hyagratamā matā |",
    "678:67": "prabhāvataḥ sarvakarmāṇi kṣipraṃ kuryārthanāmataḥ ||",
    "678:68": "śucirbhūtvā śucau deśe badhnīyānmudravaraṃ prabhum |",
    "678:69": "ādau hastau tha kṛtvā vai suṣirākārasampuṭau ||",
    "678:70": "ākośaviralāṅguṣṭhau nyastāṅguṣṭhau tha sūcitau |",
    "678:71": "pañcasūcikavinyastau mudrā pañcaśikhā bhavet ||",
    "678:72": "śiraḥsthāne sadā nyastā ekasūcyātha aṅgulaiḥ |",
    "678:73": "mudrā evacīrā tu mūrdhni sthāneṣu yojitā ||",
    "678:74": "kanyasāṅgulivinyastā suśliṣṭā madhyamau tathā |",
    "678:75": "aṅguṣṭhau sūcitau ubhau ||",
    "678:76": "trisūcyākārasamāyogāt tṛśikhā mudramudāhṛtā |",
    "678:77": "sarvairaṅgulibhiryuktaiḥ ākośā suṣirasambhavaiḥ ||",
    "678:78": "śiraḥsthāne sadā nyastā mudrā śiravarā bhavet |",
    "678:79": "sa eva ucchritāṅgulyau īṣit saṅkucitāgrakau ||",
    "678:80": "mahāvīrā tu sā jñeyā mahāmudrā maharddhikā |",
    "678:81": "ete pañca mahāmudrā pūrvaṃ jinavaraistadā ||",
    "678:82": "nirdiṣṭā sarvamudrāṇāṃ kathayanti manīṣiṇau |",
    "678:83": "jyeṣṭhā mudramukhyanāṃ + + + + + + mudritām ||",
    "678:84": "lokottarāṃ tu sarvā vai laukikānāṃ ca sarvataḥ |",
    "678:85": "etā pañca mahāmudrāḥ prayogā siddhihetavaḥ ||",
    "678:86": "susiddhā siddhatamā hyetā agrā jyeṣṭhāśca bhāṣitā |",
    "678:87": "mañjughoṣasya mūrdhajā prabhāvātyadbhutaceṣṭitā ||",
    "678:88": "yāvanti saugatā mudrā sarveṣāṃ siddhihetavaḥ |",
    "678:89": "mudrā mudreti vikhyātā śrīmantaṃ kisalayodbhavam ||",
    "678:90": "mañjughoṣasya mūrdhajaṃ mahāpuṇyatamaṃ śivam |",
    "678:91": "yaṃ badhvā mahāsattvā niyataṃ bodhimavāpnuyāt ||",
    "678:92": "mahāmukhyāvataṃsaṃ taṃ śrāddham avikalendriyam |",
    "678:93": "sadā yajñaṃ prājñayuktaṃ ca vidhivat karmamācaret ||",
    "678:94": "tādṛśena tu yuktena sattvenaiva suyojitā |",
    "678:95": "mudreyaṃ kurute hyarthāṃ yatheṣṭā cāpi puṣkalām ||",
    "678:96": "upadeśāttu vidvāṃsaḥ matimanto'rthasādhakāḥ |",
    "678:97": "ācāryasammatā loke śiṣyā grāhyāstu sarvadā ||",
    "678:98": "vidhivat karmadṛṣṭena puruṣeṇeha bhaktitaḥ |",
    "678:99": "mahāyānagatairnityaṃ mudreyaṃ samprayujyate ||",
    "678:100": "sarveṣāṃ tu mudrāṇāṃ tridhā mantreṣu yojitām |",
    "678:101": "agrā hyagratamā loke ete mudrā prabhāvataḥ ||",
    "678:102": "siddhyartthaṃ siddhikāmānāṃ tathā mantraiḥ suyojitām |",
    "678:103": "kṣipramarthakarā hyete sarvasaukhyaphalapradāḥ ||",
    "678:104": "mañjughoṣaḥ svayaṃ tiṣṭhenmudrairetaiḥ samāhita |",
    "678:105": "yasmiṃ sthāne tu vaścaitāḥ svayaṃ mañjuravaḥ sadā ||",
    "678:106": "rakṣā hyagrāṃ prakalpīta jinaputro maharddhikaḥ |",
    "678:107": "bālarūpī mahātmā vai viścarūpī maharddhikaḥ ||",
    "678:108": "bahurūpī ca sattvānāṃ mudrārūpī tha dehinām |",
    "678:109": "bāliśānāṃ tu sattvānāṃ saṃsārārṇavacāriṇām ||",
    "678:110": "teṣāmarthakaraḥ kṣipraṃ mudrārūpeṇa tiṣṭhate |",
    "678:111": "mañjughoṣasya śirajāḥ sarvamūrdhni pratiṣṭhitā ||",
    "678:112": "sarvārthasampadā hyete japtamātraistu yojitā |",
    "678:113": "mūlamantreṇa saṃyuktā hṛdayasyānugatena vā ||",
    "678:114": "sarve saugatibhiśca mantraibhiśca suyojitā |",
    "678:115": "ye tu abjakule mantrā vajriṇe cāpi kapardine ||",
    "678:116": "sarvaiśca laukikaiścāpi mudrairyuktārthaphalapradā |",
    "678:117": "ete pañca mahāmudrā mantrayuktārthaphalapradā ||",
    "678:118": "vikalpyā mantragatāṃ tyajya mudrairvātha phalapradā|",
    "678:119": "mahārakṣā mahāpuṇyā baddhamātreṇa dehinām ||",
    "678:120": "smaritaihyebhirmahāmudrairmahārakṣā vidhīyate |",
    "678:121": "kaḥ punarjaptamātraistu mantramudrāsamāśritaiḥ ||",
    "678:122": "yāvad vā jāpinaḥ sarve niyataṃ bodhimāpnuyāt |",
    "678:123": "apare tu mahāmudrāḥ śūlapaṭṭiśasambhavāḥ ||",
    "678:124": "mahāśūlo'tha mudrāṇāṃ ghoradāruṇamucyate |",
    "678:125": "krodharājena mukhyena yamānteneha yojitā ||",
    "678:126": "karoti vividhāṃ karmāṃ dāruṇāṃ prāṇarodhinām |",
    "678:127": "mahābhayapradāṃ mudrāṃ vipasyasyāpi mahātmane ||",
    "678:128": "duṣṭasattvāṃ vināśāya sṛṣṭāstṛbhavālaye |",
    "678:129": "taireva yojitā mantrā vividhāṃ mudramāśṛtā ||",
    "678:130": "teṣāṃ vināśanāyaiva sṛṣṭā jinavaraiḥ sadā |",
    "678:131": "mantracaryārtthayuktāyāḥ śāsanārthāya kalpitā ||",
    "678:132": "vihitā lokanāthaistu mudrā tantrārtthadarśanā |",
    "678:133": "duṣṭasattvaprayuktānāṃ garakilbiṣarogadām ||",
    "678:134": "teṣāṃ nirnāśanārthaiva uktāṃ sarvāthakarmikām |",
    "678:135": "yamaśāsananāśāya mṛtyupāśāya mokṣaṇāḥ||",
    "678:136": "nityaṃ prāṇaharā mudrā prayuktā mantrayojitā |",
    "678:137": "yamadūtaharā puṇyā mṛtyurnāśanī smṛtā ||",
    "678:138": "yamaśāsananītāmānetā prāṇadā smṛtā |",
    "678:139": "sarvaroganivāśārthaṃ yamasyāpi bhayapradā ||",
    "678:140": "munimukhyaistathā yuktā prāṇasandhāraṇī hitā |",
    "678:141": "śāsane'smin prasannānāṃ hitā rakṣā vidhīyate ||",
    "678:142": "saphalā nāśanī duṣṭāṃ gītā mañjurave hitā |",
    "678:143": "sarvārthaprāpaṇī devī mahāmudrā pragīyate ||",
    "678:144": "mahāpraharaṇe tvāhuḥ aparā mudraparāvarā |",
    "678:145": "tathaiva hastau saṃnyasya tarjanyau pāśasambhavau ||",
    "678:146": "kanyasau sūcayennityaṃ muṣṭiyogena yojitau |",
    "678:147": "hastau sampuṭitau nityau aṅguṣṭhābucchritāvubhau ||",
    "678:148": "eṣa mudrā mahāpuṇyā mahāśūle samāgatā |",
    "678:149": "vividhā lokanāthaistu vicitrapraharaṇodbhavā ||",
    "678:150": "yo yasya cintayejjāpī śatroḥ praharaṇāni vai |",
    "678:151": "tenaiva cchindayed gātraṃ cittotpādācca tad bhavet ||",
    "678:152": "niyataṃ nāśayecchatruṃ mudrā mantrāśca yojitā |",
    "678:153": "nihanyācchatrugaṇāṃ sarvāṃmantrāścāpi maharddhikām ||",
    "678:154": "yamadūtagaṇāṃ vighnāṃ grahāṃścāpi samātarām |",
    "678:155": "pūtanāskandarudraśca pretāṃścāpi maharddhikām ||",
    "678:156": "japtā vaivasvatāṃ lokāṃ kṛtsnāṃ caiva savāsavām |",
    "678:157": "yamāntakakrodharājena nānyaṃ mantraṃ prayojayet ||",
    "678:158": "mudrairetaiḥ prayuñjīta mahāśūlasamaistadā |",
    "678:159": "sadyaṃ vaivasvataṃ hanyāt kaḥ punarbhuvi mānuṣām ||",
    "678:160": "sarvapraharaṇī mudrāṃ sarvaduṣṭāṃ vināśinīm |",
    "678:161": "vihitā lokamukhyaistu sambuddhairdvipadottamaiḥ ||",
    "678:162": "tathaiva hastau saṃnyasta madhyamāṃ śṛtya kārayet |",
    "678:163": "tathaiva hastau kṛtveha muṣṭiyogena kārayet ||",
    "678:164": "aṅguṣṭhāgrau tu pīḍitau |",
    "678:165": "suṣirāvāṅgulisaṃyuktau madhyāṅgulyasamucchritau ||",
    "678:166": "sūcikāgrau tathā nityau tarjanyāṅgulimāśritau |",
    "678:167": "eṣā mudrā varā ghorā śūletyāhurmunivarāḥ ||",
    "678:168": "mahāśūlā bhavet sādhuḥ tarjanyākuñcitāvubhau |",
    "678:169": "visṛtaiḥ paṭṭiśā jñeyā mahāmudravarā parā ||",
    "678:170": "tadeva saṅkucāgrau tu aṅgulyāstribhirucchritā |",
    "678:171": "eṣa sā triśūlamudreti pravadanti manīṣiṇaḥ ||",
    "678:172": "vicitrapraharaṇā jñeyā aṅguṣṭhāvubhayocchritau |",
    "678:173": "mahāśūlasamā hyete mahāvīryā bhayānakāḥ ||",
    "678:174": "pāpasattvavināśāya tantre'smiṃ mañjurave vare |",
    "678:175": "durdāntadamitā hyetā mahāmudrādbhutaceṣṭitā ||",
    "678:176": "raudraprāṇaharā te vikṛtākārasambhavā |",
    "678:177": "mahāghoratamā raudrā mahākrūratamāhitā ||",
    "678:178": "mahāghoravarā jyeṣṭhā bahurūpiṇyaḥ prakāśitā |",
    "678:179": "sarvatra jāpino buddhā jarāvyādhivivarjitā ||",
    "678:180": "vicaranti imāṃ lokāṃ saṃsiddhā jāpinaḥ sadā |",
    "678:181": "vihitā mṛtyunāśāya sambuddhairmunipuṅgavaiḥ ||",
    "678:182": "jarāvyādhivināśinyaḥ mṛtyunāśāya saṃsṛjet |",
    "678:183": "yojitā mantribhiḥ kṣipraṃ kṛtāntasyāpi bhayānakā ||",
    "678:184": "sṛjet prabhuvaraḥ śrīmāṃ śuddhāvāsapure vare |",
    "678:185": "munisattamaje mudrā śākyasiṃhe narottame ||",
    "678:186": "na buddhā mantra bhāṣante na mudrā krūrakarmiṇām |",
    "678:187": "sattvakāraṇavātsalyāt sarvajñārthaprapūraṇā ||",
    "678:188": "ṛddhivikrīḍanārtthā vā bodhisambhārakāraṇā |",
    "678:189": "upāyasattvavaineyā mahāyānāgraniyojanā ||",
    "678:190": "mahāsaṃsārapūraṇā |",
    "678:191": "adhimukti vasāṃ sattvāṃ mantramudrāmudāhṛtām ||",
    "678:192": "ākāśa ceti yā buddhā na buddhā vācāya kalpitā |",
    "678:193": "niḥprapañcārthayuktānāṃ kutaḥ saṅkalpagocaram ||",
    "678:194": "dharmadhātusamā niṣṭhā bhūtakoṭisamā ca yā |",
    "678:195": "mantrayuktānāṃ niṣṭhā mudrā samudritā ||",
    "678:196": "kathayanti bhavāṅgānāṃ muktyarthaṃ hetavāṃ sadā |",
    "678:197": "sarvajñamudramākhyātā sarvajñānārthaprapūraṇā ||",
    "678:198": "yuktiyuktārthapūjārthaṃ mudrāmudramudāhṛtā |",
    "678:199": "buddhaiśca buddhaputraiśca acintyācintyagocaraiḥ ||",
    "678:200": "sarvajñadarśino mudrā uṣṇīṣādyāḥ prabhāvitāḥ |",
    "678:201": "avalokitamudrā tu vajrapāṇe tha laukikāḥ ||",
    "678:202": "kathitāḥ kathayiṣyanti śreyasārthaṃ hi dehinām |",
    "678:203": "yāvad buddhasutairmudrā muniśreṣṭhaiśca bhāṣitāḥ ||",
    "678:204": "sarvārthapūraṇā mudrā prabhāvācintacintitā |",
    "678:205": "vikalpārthaṃ hi bhūtānāṃ tridhā mantrāstu bhāṣitā ||",
    "678:206": "eka eva bhavenmantraḥ yo buddhaistu bhāṣitaḥ |",
    "678:207": "saugatārthaṃ tu mantrāṇāṃ mantro hyekaḥ pragīyate ||",
    "678:208": "uṣṇīṣādhipatiḥ śrīmāṃ ekavarṇautha vi sadā |",
    "678:209": "cakravartī bhavennityaṃ takāro rephasaṃyuta ||",
    "678:210": "ūkārasahito nityaṃ yukto'tha pragīyate |",
    "678:211": "sa bhaveccakriṇaḥ śrīmāṃ buddhānāṃ mūrddhajo varaḥ ||",
    "678:212": "bhāparaṃ mantramityāhurbuddhaputrasya dhīmataḥ |",
    "678:213": "prabhāvāt tatsamo jñeyaḥ makāro'ntyārttha gīyate ||",
    "678:214": "mañjughoṣasya vikhyātaḥ hṛdayo'yaṃ buddhamūrdhnajaḥ |",
    "678:215": "prabhāvātiśayo jñeyaḥ mahāpuṇya maharddhikaḥ ||",
    "678:216": "sarvārthapūraṇo mantraḥ |",
    "678:217": "mudrā pañcaśikhopetau ubhayārthārthapūraṇau ||",
    "678:218": "mudrā pañcaśikhā vāpi makāre cāpi yojitau |",
    "678:219": "paramārthaṃ bodhayeccārthaṃ ihaivārthaṃ tu bhogadau ||",
    "678:220": "aparaṃ mantramityāhuḥ |",
    "678:221": "jakāraṃ rephasaṃyuktaṃ avoṣmārthapūjitam ||",
    "678:222": "eṣa mantravaro hyagraḥ abjaketo'tha mūrdhnajaḥ |",
    "678:223": "mudre padmavare yukto āryā puṣṭyārthajanminām ||",
    "678:224": "jāpināṃ karmasiddhiṃ tu kuryāt sarvārthasampadām |",
    "678:225": "aparaṃ vajriṇe mantrāṃ hraṃṅkāraṃ bāhumūrdhajam ||",
    "678:226": "eṣa mantravaro hyagraḥ caṇḍo'tha gīyate |",
    "678:227": "prayukto vajrālaye mudre kuryāt prāyārthakarmiṇām ||",
    "678:228": "durdāntadamako ghoro mantro'yaṃ nāśahetavaḥ |",
    "678:229": "uktārthaṃ śāsanārthaṃ ca yathoktaṃ vidhimācaret ||",
    "678:230": "na kuryāt pāpakarmāṇi sattvanigrahamādarāt |",
    "678:231": "na yojayenmantravaraṃ nityaṃ saumyasattveṣu nityaśa ||",
    "678:232": "nāparādhye'lpadoṣeṇa sattvanāśayatotsṛjet |",
    "678:233": "na kuryādādarānmohādalpadoṣeṣu jantuṣu ||",
    "678:234": "śāsane duṣṭacittānāṃ aprasannāṃ prasadanām |",
    "678:235": "vinayārthaṃ tu sattvānāṃ damanārthaṃ piśitāśinām ||",
    "678:236": "nigrahārthaṃ tu duṣṭānāṃ saumyasattvaprasādanām |",
    "678:237": "ukto mantravaro hyagraḥ na kuryāt prāṇāntikaṃ kadā ||",
    "678:238": "sarvalaukikamantrāṇāṃ vajriṇe ca maharddhikām |",
    "678:239": "agro mantravaro hyuktaḥ sarvalaukikadevatām ||",
    "678:240": "aparo mantravaro hyeṣa sarvalaukikadevatām |",
    "678:241": "mantrāṇāṃ mūrdhnajo jñeyaḥ śiva ekākṣaro hyataḥ ||",
    "678:242": "īśvaraḥ sarvalokānāṃ mantrāṇāṃ tu laukikāṃ prabhuḥ |",
    "678:243": "parameśvaramityāhuḥ svakāro tā vidurbudhāḥ ||",
    "678:244": "sarvamantrāstu gīyante yāvantyo laukikāḥ smṛtāḥ |",
    "678:245": "sarve te yatra vai mantre nibaddhā sarvatra pūjitā ||",
    "678:246": "vihitā munivarai hyetā mudrā sarvatra yojitā |",
    "678:247": "matā śivatamā śreṣṭhā laukikāgrā samāhitā ||",
    "678:248": "īśvarādyāntarbhūtā vai vipaśyagrahamātarām |",
    "678:249": "kaṭapūtanayakṣādyāṃ rākṣasāṃ piśitāśinām ||",
    "678:250": "garuḍadhvajaviṣṇośca brahmaṇaścāpi kīrtitā |",
    "678:251": "mudrā hyetāḥ samādiṣṭā durdāntadamane hitā ||",
    "678:252": "praśastā maṅgalā hyetā mudrā hyuktā manīṣibhiḥ |",
    "678:253": "vaśyāveṣaṇabhūtānāṃ ākṛṣṭā hetavohitām ||",
    "678:254": "vivikte tu sadā deśe śuklapuṣpaiḥ suśobhite |",
    "678:255": "sumṛṣṭe siddhagandhaistu śvetacandanakuṅkumaiḥ ||",
    "678:256": "jātīkusumamālābhiḥ abhyarcya sugataṃ prabhum |",
    "678:257": "śākyasiṃhaṃ mahāpuṇyaṃ sarvamantreśvaraṃ vibhum ||",
    "678:258": "sarvajñaṃ sarvadā bhaktyā praṇipatya tathāgatam |",
    "678:259": "mantranāthaṃ ca lokeśaṃ vajriṇaṃ cāpi śaktitaḥ ||",
    "678:260": "mañjuśriyaṃ mahātmānaṃ dharmadhātveśvaraṃ gurum |",
    "678:261": "sarvaṃ buddhasutāṃ buddhāṃ anupūrvyā samāhitaḥ ||",
    "678:262": "kuśaviṇḍe pallave caiva sakṣīare sārdre suśobhane |",
    "678:263": "upaviṣṭaḥ prāṅmukhaḥ śuciḥ ||",
    "678:264": "udaṅmukhaḥ śāntikarme tu paścādāhvānane na mukhe |",
    "678:265": "na kuryuḥ sarvakarmāṇi yathādaivatamandirām ||",
    "678:266": "pravṛttaḥ sarvabhūteṣu dayāvāṃ mudrakarmaṇi |",
    "678:267": "sarvatra yojitā mudrā kuryāt sarvasādhanam ||",
    "678:268": "pūrvābhimukhe pauṣṭikaṃ karma mantrāṇāmānayane dhruvam |",
    "678:269": "paścānmukhe tu kurvīta vaśyārthaṃ sarvabhautikam ||",
    "678:270": "udaṅmukhe śāntikaṃ vindyāt sarvavyādhipraṇāśane |",
    "678:271": "dakṣiṇe pāpakarmaṃ tu na kuryāt prāṇāntikaṃ sadā ||",
    "678:272": "ūrdhvaṃ vighnanāśaṃ tu uttiṣṭhottamasiddhidaḥ |",
    "678:273": "asurapure karma pātālādhipate tadā ||",
    "678:274": "aghomukhaśca kurvīta sarvatrāpratipūjitā |",
    "678:275": "vidikṣu ca sarvatra yathā yathā ca samāsṛtā ||",
    "678:276": "teṣu teṣu kurvīta sidhyante sarvadehinām |",
    "678:277": "kuryāt sarvatra mudrāṇāṃ vidhihomasamā japī ||",
    "678:278": "tatrasthāṃ siddhimāyānti tanmukhāścāpi mudritā |",
    "678:279": "vidhiḥ śreṣṭhaḥ kathyatāṃ tāṃ nibodhatām ||",
    "678:280": "śucirvastraśucirbhūtvā sukhaśaucasamāhitaḥ |",
    "678:281": "imāṃ mudrāṃ prayuñjīta sarvārthāṃ ca susamādhikām ||",
    "678:282": "hastāvuddhṛtya gandhaiśca śvetacandanakuṅkumaiḥ |",
    "678:283": "sudhūpaiḥ prāṇyaṅgarahitaiḥ karpūrāgarucandanaiḥ ||",
    "678:284": "yuktikuṅkumamukhyaiśca kuryāddhūmavaraṃ vidā |",
    "678:285": "nivedya vividhā karmāṃ ācared vidhivat sadā ||",
    "678:286": "ācaret pūrvanirdiṣṭaṃ karmaṃ sarvatra kalpabhāṣitam |",
    "678:287": "prāṅmukho'tha tato bhūtvā ubhau hastau susampuṭau ||",
    "678:288": "miśrīkṛtāṃ tato'nyonyāṃ aṅgulyā veṇitaḥ sthitau |",
    "678:289": "madhyamau kanyasau jyaṣṭhau anāmikāgrau ca yojitau ||",
    "678:290": "aṅguṣṭhau niścalau jñeyau samau cāpi pratiṣṭhitau |",
    "678:291": "śirasthāne tadā kuryā lalāṭadeśe tu bhaktitaḥ ||",
    "678:292": "namaskāraṃ tathā mantraṃ ṣaḍvarṇotha yojitām |",
    "678:293": "om vākyeda namaḥ |",
    "678:294": "vākyaṃ svāhākāravarjitam ||",
    "678:295": "huṅkārāpagataṃ śreṣṭhaṃ phaṭkārāpagataṃ sadā |",
    "678:296": "pavitraṃ maṅgalaṃ jyeṣṭhaṃ hṛdayaṃ tu sadā japet ||",
    "678:297": "eṣa mañjuvara ! śreṣṭhaṃ bālarūpisurūpiṇe |",
    "678:298": "paścānme viśvarūpe tu hṛdayo'yaṃ prakīrtyate ||",
    "678:299": "ṣaḍete ṣaḍakṣarā jñeyā mantrā śreṣṭhā hṛdayottamā |",
    "678:300": "teṣāmagratarā hyeṣā pravṛttaḥ sarvakarmasu ||",
    "678:301": "idaṃ mudrottamaṃ mantraṃ kuryāt sarvakarmasu |",
    "678:302": "mūrdhni sthāne dattvā lalāṭoddeśe tu yuktitaḥ ||",
    "678:303": "madhyamāṅgulyaṃ tu cāled vaśyārthaṃ sārvabhautikam |",
    "678:304": "aṅguṣṭhāgrāvubhau nāmyau ākṛṣṭārthaṃ ca devatām ||",
    "678:305": "taireva visṛtau nityaṃ visarjyaṃ mantradevatām |",
    "678:306": "madhyajyeṣṭhau tathā śrāvakāṃśca munivaram ||",
    "678:307": "tarjanyau kuñcitau nityau bodhisattvāṃ kuliśodbhavām |",
    "678:308": "daśabhūmyeśvarā ye ca āhvayante na saṃśayam ||",
    "678:309": "kanyasāṅgulisaṃyuktā ākuñcyāt sarāhvaye |",
    "678:310": "yakṣarākṣasapretāṃśca kūṣmāṇḍā kaṭapūtanām ||",
    "678:311": "daityadānavasaṅghāṃśca yakṣiṇyāśca dhanadapriyā |",
    "678:312": "mātṛvat kurute hyetāṃ mudreyaṃ samprapūjitā ||",
    "678:313": "arthānarthāṃ tathā nityamiṣṭāniṣṭā phalapradām |",
    "678:314": "mahāmudreti vikhyātā gīyate tṛbhavālaye ||",
    "678:315": "eṣa mudramahāmudrā baddhā mūrdhasu paṇḍitaḥ |",
    "678:316": "adhṛṣyaḥ sarvabhūtānāṃ bhavate nātra saṃśayaḥ ||",
    "678:317": "dūrād dūraṃ namasyanti sarvavighnavināyakā |",
    "678:318": "mahābrahmasamaṃ puṇyaṃ niyataṃ bodhimavāpnuyāditi ||",
    "678:319": "bodhisattvapiṭakāvataṃsakānmahāyānavaipulyasūtrāt",
    "678:320": "āryamañjuśriyamūlakalpāt dvicatvāriṃśa-",
    "678:321": "timaḥ mahāmudrāpaṭalavisaraḥ",
    "678:322": "parisamāpta iti ||"
}